ingredientsDesc:
Reagents:
125I GASTRIN: Synthetic gastrin 1 (1-17), buffer, bovine albumin, red dye. £ 37 kBq (£ 1 μCi). Reconstitute with 10 ml of distilled water.
Antiserum: Anti-gastrin rabbit antiserum, buffer, normal rabbit serum, bovine albumin, preservative, blue dye. Reconstitute with 30 ml of distilled water.
STANDARDS: Synthetic gastrin 1, (1-17), buffer bovine albumin, sodium azide. 20-60-150-500-1500 μU/ml*. Reconstitute with 1 ml of distilled water.
0 STANDARD: Buffer, bovine albumin, sodium azide. Reconstitute with 5 ml of distilled water.
IMMUNOPRECIPITATING REAGENT: Insoluble complex of anti-rabbit IgG sheep serum and non-immunized rabbit IgG, buffer, polyethylene glycol, sodium azide.
